  "system": {
    "description": "<p>A street-level villain with the ability to generate localised shockwaves by striking surfaces. She runs a protection racket across three city districts and is fiercely territorial. Shatter is pragmatic and genuinely community-minded in a warped way — she keeps harder criminals out of her territory, which makes her relationship with law enforcement complicated. Heroes who approach her diplomatically find a more nuanced conversation than expected.</p>",
